{
  "id": "adv_main_03_04_03",
  "title": "BIG4編1章18話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――カフェでの一件の後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the incident at the cafe",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、ちょっといいか？　どりきゅんについて\n橋本さんと調べたから参考として聞いてほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ can I have a minute of your time? About DoriKyun‚\nHashimoto-san and I looked into them‚ so I want you to hear this as a reference.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "昨日、さとみちゃんとデートして\nゲットした情報だよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The information you got from your date\nwith Satomi-san yesterday‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.7106912789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "だから、それは誤解だって言ってるだろ……ん？\nえーと、琴乃？　渚？　すず……？　どうした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I’m telling you it’s a misunderstanding… Huh?\nUh‚ Kotono? Nagisa? Suzu…? What’s wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.470295437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Satomi-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1369638839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "デートですってーーー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re datingーーー!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.8702953099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 30.6328133899
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん、どーどー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan‚ calm down!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6328133899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "爆弾を放り込んだ本人が何言ってますの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you saying after dropping a bomb like that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.6328133899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん。詳しく聞かせて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san. Tell us more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4678483883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私は別に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Well‚ I’m not really…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.6345150549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、皆さん。その件は後で私が説明しますから\nまずはお話を聞きましょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay okay‚ everyone. I'll explain that later‚\nso let’s listen to what he has to say first‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9011832555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "は～い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9678506771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、私からお話しさせてもらいますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ allow me to explain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0964672009,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 55.8169435024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんですが……元々凄まじいグループでしたが\n活動を再開してからは勢いがパワーアップしてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "DoriKyun… they were an amazing group to begin with‚\nbut their momentum has powered up even more since they resumed activities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "以前からライブバトルの回数は、アイドル界最多でした\nでも、そのペースは休止前よりもさらに増してるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’ve always had the most live battles in the idol world‚\nbut that pace has increased even more than before their hiatus.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.6333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "最近の活動を見た限り、元々多かった過激なファンが\nさらに増えて、結束力が強くなってますわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From what I’ve seen of their recent activities‚ they have even more\nradical fans than before‚ and their solidarity has become stronger.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5790877422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、なんでどりきゅんはお休みしてたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the first place‚ why did DoriKyun take a break?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8545766593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "いろいろな噂は立っていますが\n本当の理由は明かされていませんよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There have been a lot of rumors‚\nbut the real reason has never been revealed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.9879127981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですよね。なので今回は\n情報通から聞いた情報をまとめてみました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. So this time‚\nI’ve compiled information from various sources.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1000035604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_unrest-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 102.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-stm005.m4a",
      "text": "原因は、端的に言えば……\nライブバトルでアイドルを潰し過ぎたから、みたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason‚ in short‚ is…\nthey crushed too many idols in live battles.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.8000035604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ひぇっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eek!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6862969956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "因果関係が分かるような分からないような……\n詳しく教えてもらえますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not sure if I understand the cause and effect…\nCan you elaborate?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7723919472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-stm006.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトルの影響で、大小様々な事務所から\n番組やライブでの共演を次々とNGにされたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A lot of production companies‚ big and small‚\nrefused to work with them on programs and live shows.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.9000030518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-stm007.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんのお二人はそんな状況でもまるで平然と\nしていたようですが……事務所が待ったをかけたようで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The two members of DoriKyun seemed indifferent to the situation‚\nbut… it seems like their agency put a stop to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1333318075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-stm008.m4a",
      "text": "いったん落ち着いた方がいい、と半ば無理やり\n休止させた……というのが真実のようですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They were told that it was better to calm down for a while‚\nand were forced to take a break… That seems to be the truth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どうやら、どりきゅんと事務所の間には\nある程度の温度差があるようだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well I can see the difference of how DoriKyun and\ntheir agency deal with the situation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7333348593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "なんというか……アイドルとは思えないくらい\nアグレッシブですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s… incredibly aggressive\nfor idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7852352064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 153.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-stm009.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよね。そして休止後、彼女達は\n事務所の許可なしに動画チャンネルを始めました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. And after their hiatus‚ they started a video channel\nwithout their agency’s permission.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_03-stm010.m4a",
      "text": "初めこそ事務所と揉めたものの\n早々にとてつもない人気チャンネルになって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At first‚ they had some trouble with their agency‚\nbut it quickly became a tremendously popular channel…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.100001526,
